Class BgpPassivePeerConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.BgpPeerConfig
      • org.batfish.datamodel.BgpPassivePeerConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class BgpPassivePeerConfig
extends BgpPeerConfig
    Represents a passive BGP config, which allows peering with multiple remote peers, but cannot initiate connections.
